No.1/34/1/2015-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 7th March, 2015
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 5th March, 2015, Shri
Raosaheb Dadarao Danve relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Consumer Affairs, Food and Public Distribution.
(S.G.P. Verghese)
for Cabinet Secretary
Tele : 2301 1791
Fax: 2379 3504
E-mail: verghese.sgp@nic.in
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to the Vice-Chairperson, NITI Aayog.
(S.G.P. Verghese)
for Cabinet Secretary

Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.

(S.G.P. Verghese)
